h3. AIS Receiver and DSC in One Package
AIS receiver and DSC (Class-H) function add further assurance for safety at sea. With the integrated AIS receiver, vessel traffic information is shown on the display. The AIS target call function allows you to easily set up a DSC individual call. Distress calls can be made with the rear panel button.
!https://www.icomeurope.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/AIS_screen-290x300.png|thumbnail!

The IC-M94DE’s 6 watts of transmit power provides extended communication range for the user. The supplied 2400 mAh (typical) high capacity Li-ion battery, BP-306 provides 10 hours of operating time, under normal conditions*.
* Approximate, typical operation with 5:5:90 duty ratio.
